                            <comment id="17847095" author="knoguchi" created="Thu, 16 May 2024 21:01:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, original patch had extra comma causing the compile error for TestFlatten.java. &lt;br/&gt;
Uploaded pig-5453-v02.patch.&#160; &#160;To fix the broken trunk, I pushed the change.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17847097" author="daijy" created="Thu, 16 May 2024 21:03:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17847376" author="knoguchi" created="Fri, 17 May 2024 17:02:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While tracking multiple jiras, I missed that this patch was not put through full unit/e2e tests.&#160; &#160;(Thus the previous syntax error.)&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After fixing the simple syntax error, saw a couple of regression test failures.&#160; At this point, reverting the patch while I debug and come up with a new patch.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So sorry.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
